sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Middleware as Middleware: auth:sanctum
    participant Request as ChangePasswordRequest
    participant Controller as ChangePasswordController
    participant User as User (Model)
    participant Token as PersonalAccessToken
    participant DB as Database

    Client->>Middleware: PUT /api/password
    Middleware->>Middleware: Verify Sanctum token

    alt Invalid or missing token
        Middleware-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized
    end

    Middleware->>Request: Validate input

    Note over Request: Rules:<br/>current_password: required, current_password<br/>password: required, min:8, confirmed

    alt Validation fails (missing fields, weak password, mismatch)
        Request-->>Client: 422 Validation errors
    end

    alt Current password is wrong
        Request-->>Client: 422 {"current_password": ["The current password is incorrect."]}
    end

    Request->>Controller: __invoke(ChangePasswordRequest)

    Controller->>User: update(['password' => newPassword])
    User->>DB: UPDATE users SET password = hashed_value
    DB-->>User: OK

    Note over Controller: Invalidate other tokens

    Controller->>Token: tokens()->where('id', '!=', currentToken)->delete()
    Token->>DB: DELETE FROM personal_access_tokens<br/>WHERE tokenable_id = user_id<br/>AND id != current_token_id
    DB-->>Token: OK

    Controller-->>Client: 200 {"message": "Password changed successfully."}
